{"tid":417884,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]公司黎左箱高級桃","createTime":"2017-09-29T05:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T07:49:37.000Z","uid":124804,"like":363,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"893aad6b41abb5f309116a28fdceb8afdf3618cf","tid":417884,"uid":124804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:54:45.000Z","msg":"話說公司做出版行業 中秋就會有印刷廠送d生果月餅上黎<br />\n今年有一間送左箱桃 未開箱已經好香 箱印有長野信州logo<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/s640x640/sh0.08/e35/20969005_112397516125596_5592782112202686464_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fs640x640%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2F20969005_112397516125596_5592782112202686464_n.jpg&h=e7399467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係呢一箱<br />\n<br />\n啲同事圍住晒等開箱<br />\n之後腦細就行左入黎 成箱拎走左<br />\n好似話要拎去分俾親戚同屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但以我地所知 腦細好似同親戚反晒面咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算唔算侵佔公司財物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申: 冇實物相，因為太快未影得切就拎走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"5240bf41723c94a91f9b7fa852080d561e84d4b1","tid":417884,"uid":94090,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"咁所以呢？"},{"pid":"29f3bf529512c981a26048ddf3f7a2394181b644","tid":417884,"uid":53223,"like":281,"dislike":5,"score":276,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"公司屬於老細嫁wor，你哋員工有股份？"},{"pid":"9768c2fc4a00f39b7be693be927d002ba9f54d09","tid":417884,"uid":142314,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"好心老細中秋識做啦"},{"pid":"2c833070ea5e0c0b0eb922ff4aebbfd752c31b12","tid":417884,"uid":46595,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"佢係老闆你吹得佢帳?"},{"pid":"cea382177063e1f604aa0